## 🚀 Sections

| Section | Description |
|---|---|
| **Hero** | Name, typed role, CTA buttons, tech badges, profile photo |
| **Stats** | Animated counters — projects, CGPA, technologies, graduation year |
| **About Me** | Background, philosophy, target roles |
| **Technical Matrix** | 4 skill categories with animated progress bars |
| **Featured Projects** | 3 production projects with banner, features, stack, and links |
| **Timeline** | Education track + accolades and certifications |
| **Get In Touch** | Contact form + profile card with social links |

